Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.15,0:00:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.76,0:00:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You're that irregular everyone's been talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using strange attacks like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. She's only unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the ally of rationality and the enemy of needless conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.65,0:01:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.39,0:01:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Kyoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're trying to pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my leave for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.28,0:01:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wise choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come here to save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times must I tell you before you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already warned you countless times...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to stop coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:02:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you intend to continue acting foolish...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I won't show any mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind her. She's surely planning something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must exercise caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akemi Homura. Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be okay for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's completely black.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad. If it continues to collect taint...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Witch may revive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be fine, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my job as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, in order to purify your Soul Gem any further,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll need to find another Grief Seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really that important to keep this thing purified?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Kyoko is powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:05:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By keeping your Soul Gem pure, you can use as much magic as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Kyoko remains so powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I can't just sacrifice a human being for the sake of a Grief Seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more magic you use, the more your Grief Seed will become tainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka, if you don't collect any more Grief Seeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then there's no way you'll defeat Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... Is that really the only way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami-san didn't have that many Grief Seeds, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was still able to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the big difference between myself and her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sucks! It's so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko is not only talented, but also a veteran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, on the other hand, have no experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if we were to compare talent, then there is someone who's more talented than Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? And who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname Madoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. So if you truly wish to defeat Kyoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would need to bring Madoka into the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All she needs to do is form a contract with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't possibly drag her into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo. What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heck are you talking about?{TLC Note: What kind of wind are you blowing now?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only you are worthy of the title "Magical Girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki Sayaka won't be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how should we deal with Sayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave her alone, she'll just start another fight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to think of a peaceful method.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay put and leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have one last question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you? {TL: what are you?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In two weeks "Walpurgis Night" will come to this city. {TL: Its a night where all the Witches get a power boost and become l33t}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we just need to defeat her; then, I can leave this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, it's all on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Walpurgis Night", eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's going to be difficult to handle on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we team up, we may have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. We've spent too much time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can catch that familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sayaka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue to search for Witches,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll meet that girl again, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if we do meet with her again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,could you two talk things over?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, you two will end up arguing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arguing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really what you thought last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a fight to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't that serious at the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:09:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But by the end, we just wanted to kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you expect me to "talk things over"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's someone who thinks of human beings as nothing more than a nest for Grief Seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you expect us to calmly talk things over?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan, you became a Magical Girl to hunt Witches, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a Witch, but a Magical Girl like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you two try, I know we can all be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may have different methods than she does, but you both want to hunt Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for Homura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mami-san, too. If she hadn't argued with Homura-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw what happened, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She waited until Mami-san died before coming to defeat the Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted that Grief Seed so badly that she didn't care if Mami-san died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That transfer student and Kyoko... they're both the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They only think about themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami-san was an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every other Magical Girl is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though that familiar wasn't powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it could still kill someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know who its target may be. It could even be your mom and dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may even be Ta-kun! {tl: uhhh my ears suck, so it might not be 'ta-kun'}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you just let that happen, Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll forgive them for doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not {\i1}just{\i0} fighting Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm using my powers to protect those who are dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if something far more vicious than a Witch were to appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it is a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something, Kyubei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I can say is that it's very foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan has no chance of defeating Akemi Homura nor Sakura Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how many times I tell her, she just won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend is in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't seem to have any ill intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the more she tries to do the right thing, the worse it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That happens a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfortunate, but when you do that, it doesn't always feel like you're doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If everyone were to do what they feel is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then there'll be no more happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not doing anything wrong, and yet she can't find any happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:13:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this is delicate, so I'd suggest not interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if it's not a perfect solution, you want to try, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll need to do something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's too thoughtful, and she needs someone to do something wrong for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like telling a lie or running away from something scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after you did that, you'll realize it was the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you reach a point where you don't know what else you can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you might as well do something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How will she know it's for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it's not immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, it's not the perfect solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you rather give up on her or be misunderstood every now and then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't tell lies and you don't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been trying to do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already succeeded as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, before you become an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you need to learn when to do something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn... when to do something wrong...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a kid, you heal quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take advantage of that and use your time to make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find it useful someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're older,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be harder to make those mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As our responsibilities increase, so does the need for caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adults lead difficult lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they drink their sorrows away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to drink sake with you, too, someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Then hurry and grow up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has its rough times, but it's still fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Kamijou-san, he was discharged yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rehabilitation was successful,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the treatment was completed early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to head home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've chased him around all day, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all about this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the reason why you formed a contract with Kyubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using your only chance to wish for something on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would someone like you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who doesn't understand, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason magic exists is so that our deepest desires may become a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's worthless if you use it on someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Tomoe Mami tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there easier methods of getting a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just use the magic that you worked so hard to obtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go inside and break his arms and legs so that he can't play the violin anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it so that he'll need your help to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:17:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, he'll be all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be it his heart or his body, it's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're too much of a wimp, then I'll do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider it a favor from another Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'll let that slide...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's change our location, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, people will see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's too thoughtful, and she needs someone to do something wrong for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I possibly do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly, Sayaka's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Madoka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here, this doesn't involve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that! This isn't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess annoying people have annoying friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we discuss this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to do anything to Miki Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your way of doing things is too slow for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, she's as ready as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll take care of her. Do not interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jumping in when I finish this.{I'll wait until I'm finished eating}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, what are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was really bad, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just threw away your friend. Aren't you going to do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan... Hey, Sayaka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want this to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:20:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the fuck is going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Magical Girl can only control their bodies within a 100 meter radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 meters?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would normally keep your body nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this sort of thing rarely happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Kyubei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want Sayaka-chan to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, that person is not Sayaka, it's merely a hollow shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just threw the real Sayaka away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to use a human being's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then there'd be no way for you to fight Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Magical Girls like yourselves, your original body is merely hardware.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:21:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It serves as a container for your soul, allowing you to channel magic efficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, your soul is stored somewhere more compact and safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the one responsible for forming contracts with Magical Girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my job is to remove your souls and exchange them for Soul Gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little bastard... What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fucking around. We're basically just zombies then, aren't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's better?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get stabbed in the heart, or if you lose all the blood in your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just use magic to fix your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as your Soul Gem is there, you will never die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is much more effective than using an actual human body in a fight, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible... How could you possibly...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you girls always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I tell the truth, you react the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:22:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do humans care so much about where their soul resides?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.94,0:24:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a wish you wanted to grant so badly that you'd even accept your fate as a Magical Girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.90,0:24:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, have I not granted you that wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I face my true feelings?
